threads.title: 820-3437 No Fan Spin (Liquid)
threads.message:
When unit came in the light on the charger was super dim...i always check in a black room. When i took apart the unit and pluged charger in to get voltages the light turned green then orange. 

Some quick Readings
PPBUS_G3H = 8.58
PP3V42_G3H = 3.43
PP5V_S5 = 5.02 
PP5V_S4RS3 = 0
PP3V3_S5 = 3.33

Smc area looks clean and really the board doesnt look like it took on much water.
